p.k: Realising her and the Professor don't have much in common, Bubbles schedules a road trip with just the two of them. / When Morbucks enters the Student Body President race, Blossom sinks to her level to secure the win. / When the Professor's latest invention wreaks havoc in the house, it's up to the Powerpuff Girls to stop it before it escapes. / When Blossom can't join her favourite school club, she imagines what her life would be like if she joined other clubs.
